videos.description: Marial Shayok bursts through the lane for the layup to help build on Virginia's lead in the early going.
videos.headline: Virginia's Shayok fights through lane for layup

videos.description: Isaiah Wilkins comes up with the block and London Perrantes finishes on the other end for Virginia.
videos.headline: UVA block leads to Perrantes and-one finish

videos.description: Darius Thompson comes up with the steal for Virginia and then finishes on the other end, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Virginia's Thompson gets steal and lay-in

videos.description: Devon Hall hits from beyond the arc with the shot clock winding down to increase Virginia's second half lead.
videos.headline: Hall helps Virginia break game open

videos.description: Ben Lammers gets the feed from Corey Heyward and slams one home while drawing a foul in the process.
videos.headline: Lammers gets dunk and draws foul for Georgia Tech

videos.description: Marial Shayok gets the bucket and draws the foul to help Virginia pull away from Georgia Tech for good.
videos.headline: Shayok helps seal victory for Virginia

videos.description: Marial Shayok and London Perrantes combine for 30 points in Virginia's 62-49 win over Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Shayok, Perrantes steer Virginia to victory
